                           <locus target="#46vb">Fol. 46vb</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 46vb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘደጃዝማች፡ ወልደ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ዘአቡሁ፡ ተክለ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወእሙ፡ ወለተ፡ አናንያ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ አቡነ፡ ማማስ፡ ዘገርሕሴ፡ በዘመነ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወመስፍንነ፡ ልዑል፡ ራስ፡ ጉግሣ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ው[fol. 47ra]ጉዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ በአፈ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ቅዱስ፡ ወበአፈ፡ ፲ወ፪ ሐዋርያት። በ፲ወ፱፳ወ፬ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note states that däğğazmač Wäldä Gäbrǝʾel donated the book to the church of ʾAbunä Mamas of Gärhǝse in 1924 A.M. (= 1931/32 A.D.), in the time of King Ḫaylä Śǝllase I (r. 1930-74) and lǝʿul ras Gugsa ʾArʾaya (d. 1933, EAE II, 905-06).
The note is followed by an exhortation to the readers to pray for the donor. Two stamps are beneath the note.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Short supplication for the scribe: fol. 56va.&#xD;
- A few corrections written interlineally: e.g., fols. 45ra, 49ra.&#xD;
- Small crosses, near to the rubricated words: fols 40r, 41r. &#xD;
- Two illegible stamps: fol. 47r.&#xD;
- Many doodles (repetition of text passages or names of saints) in the upper margin, in pen: e.g., fols. 6v, 9r, 10r, 12v, 14v, 15r, 20r, 24v, 25v, 35v, 36r, 37r, 41r, 43r, 44r.</item>
